if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('base_product')
and type = 'U')
drop table base_product
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: base_product */
/*==============================================================*/
create table base_product (
ProID int identity(10000,1),
CID int not null,
PicUrl nvarchar(500) not null,
PriceR decimal(10,2) not null,
Property int not null,
Status int not null,
Name nvarchar(200) null,
Description nvarchar(1000) null,
StockNum int null,
SWeight int null,
SupplierIDs nvarchar(100) not null,
Url nvarchar(500) null,
Keyword nvarchar(100) null,
Model nvarchar(20) null,
Size nvarchar(50) null,
Code nvarchar(50) null,
BCode nvarchar(200) null,
Spec nvarchar(200) null,
BPrinc decimal(10,2) null,
PicLoc nvarchar(300) null,
UpdateTime datetime null default getdate(),
IsDel bit not null default 0,
AppTime datetime null default getdate(),
AdminID int not null,
constraint PK_BASE_PRODUCT primary key (ProID)
)
go
